    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2 Class II device assessment. Six factors appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 1. The CFD hemolysis model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device tolerance decision. Predicted RH < 1.0 across all operating points with adequate agreement to reference data. The numerical simulation campaign is considered to provide validation evidence of equivalent quality to a dedicated experimental study, given prior FDA benchmark validation of the solver. Decision: model is credible for stated COU.",
